{"tid":2236151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳靜Dada姊遇口㾗網友留言問過夜價 ರ_ರ","createTime":"2020-10-09T09:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T10:51:32.000Z","uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"c3016e1b4c29e620d85b1dd9ea6e25524023249c","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"31歲陳靜Dada姊近來努力修身及密操蜜桃臀，減肥成功，連其最強胸器34E奶都大縮水，最近身穿吊帶貼身背心，大玩濕身誘惑，當年E奶明顯大縮水，不過卻惹來網民留言問過夜價，仍然有市有價﹗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dada5_17042036445f80010c05425.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdada5_17042036445f80010c05425.png&h=550a332f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46194b1e70a6b5aa886c46c7d0c609db549bf844","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:06:09.000Z","msg":"努力修身、把長長秀髮剪短，令人煥然一新的感覺，日前她在社交網po出濕身片，坐在浴缸內的陳靜臉尖尖、手臂纖瘦，腰部卻有結實腹肌，的確比從前更fit，不過昔日的34E洶湧上圍卻不復見，上圍明顯大縮水。不過陳靜呢條濕身誘惑片，卻仍然引來網友讚索，亦有人留言：「陰公，瘦到對波都細埋」又有網友口痕手大日陳靜：「1皮嘢過夜」，被人公開問價的Dada姊唔知滿唔滿意個身價呢？"},{"pid":"34fbc8e1d7f094385ace4d0e69c323ca7888bab0","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/photogrid_plus_1602224612897_11780176615f8002984e85e-1024x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fphotogrid_plus_1602224612897_11780176615f8002984e85e-1024x1024.jpg&h=ac8e7483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民都替陳靜sis上圍縮水感到可悲，不過不少網民都大讚正又索。"},{"pid":"3258d9774b87164aaec60eff99ee66fc8398fc0a","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"曾經係32界金像獎最佳女配角得主，所以對自己要求很高，收起事業線嘅陳靜，最近因為接拍左兩部新電影，在戲內有好多動作鏡頭，希望在角色入面發揮得更好，所以最近狂做運動，經常約朋友行山，游水同做gym高強度體能訓練，還做近年興起普拉提（Pilates）是一種集合瑜伽、舞蹈和體操訓練的運動，透過各種動作強化全身肌肉耐力及矯正姿勢，達至收身及減肥功效。"},{"pid":"8038973ca38a156081b4d7e3c95c9f19a4f5571c","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":58,"score":-53,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dadachan_120554045_342378033670609_1431424387433121874_n_19778327975f7ffbb839f17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdadachan_120554045_342378033670609_1431424387433121874_n_19778327975f7ffbb839f17.jpg&h=f38dd114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中秋節上載同姨甥女合照，陳靜sis看落比之前瘦了不少。"},{"pid":"0660646dc92c6a69fa912a029d9af608c2c93954","tid":2236151,"uid":40470,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"無名氣無人識的話<br />\n<br />\n480比盡"},{"pid":"e93f1042a800192dc6548662d4b49362acb2dce2","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dadachan_119943646_2693195350897422_3464762122140948243_n_12699535225f7fffc9ee8ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdadachan_119943646_2693195350897422_3464762122140948243_n_12699535225f7fffc9ee8ea.jpg&h=4f961111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n健身可幫助陳靜sis肌肉上強化。"},{"pid":"7eea01e2e0c477c6958ee829d9fcc5703fbe621e","tid":2236151,"uid":40470,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e93f1042a800192dc6548662d4b49362acb2dce2","tid":2236151,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":30,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dadachan_119943646_2693195350897422_3464762122140948243_n_12699535225f7fffc9ee8ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdadachan_119943646_2693195